{"tid":592146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"立法補選：郭卓堅明入稟司法覆核DQ鄭泳舜 因民建聯主張「香港民主建國」","createTime":"2018-03-14T03:53:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-15T00:46:00.000Z","uid":54373,"like":28,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b79aea354e941dd0768283a7ee66ef48aa46d7ef","tid":592146,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T03:53:22.000Z","msg":"因有議員被取消資格(DQ)而觸發的立法會補選甫結束，已接二連三再現DQ呼聲，除了於港島區勝出的區諾軒被市民入稟司法覆核外，於九龍西區勝出的鄭泳舜亦不能幸免，外號「長洲覆核王」的郭卓堅今日(13日)晚上於Facebook發文，指明(14日)早將會入稟司法覆核，要求取消鄭泳舜的議員資格。<br />\n<br />\n郭卓堅指鄭泳舜違背參選時所簽署的確認書上「效忠中華人民共和國」一環，指鄭所屬的政黨民建聯主張「香港民主建港」和「香港民主建國」，認為這兩項主張等同港獨，是分裂國家的行為，故此要求法庭頒令，剝奪鄭的議員資格。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20180313/photo/bkn-20180313220228738-0313_00822_001_02b.jpg?20180313222530\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180313%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20180313220228738-0313_00822_001_02b.jpg%3F20180313222530&h=561a7976&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n郭卓堅指鄭泳舜違背參選時所簽署的確認書上「效忠中華人民共和國」一環。(郭卓堅fb)"},{"pid":"4a44d0d1195179a4579338f27143455e40810f58","tid":592146,"uid":77196,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:10:47.000Z","msg":"今次真係恭喜禮儀廉，大家鬥玩野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d90442032053c9697226d4046392d544e2eff6","tid":592146,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:20:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4370a755ad9e652fce3398c9629899cc3a7196","tid":592146,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T04:28:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00568fae1e6632908603a40a67b833e354cccde8","tid":592146,"uid":102